ces, coming with one face to these and another to those.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7179, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2526 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":482,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/02\/01\/do-not-condemn-yourself\/","url_meta":{"origin":510,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Self-Bullying: Do not condemn yourself as evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"None of you should say: My soul has been wicked. Rather, let him say: My soul has faulted.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6179, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2250 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/26\/prophet-good-akhlaq-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":510,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The Prophet teaches good character, manners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr re